<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css"
      />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/index.css" />
    <title>Task Manager|Home</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    {{>spinner}}
    <section id="login" class="login-section">
      <div class="login-area">
        <div class="crossLoginHeader">
          <h1>Welocome To Task Manager</h1>
          <div class="taskCross">
            <span class="cross"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="main-login">
          <img src="./assets/taskImg.jpg" alt="task image" />
          <form class="login-form">
            <div class="login-inputs">
              <input class="loginEmail" type="text" placeholder="Email" />
              <input class="loginPassword" type="password"
                placeholder="Password" />
            </div>
            <button class="submitBtn" type="submit">Sign in</button>
            <p>Don't have an account? <span class="loginbarlink">Sign up</span>
            </p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="signup" class="signup-section">
      <div class="signup-area">
        <div class="crossSignupHeader"><h1>Welocome To Task Manager</h1>
          <div class="taskCross">
            <span class="cross"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span>
          </div></div>

        <div class="main-signup">
          <img src="./assets/taskImg.jpg" alt="task image" />
          <form class="signup-form">
            <div class="signup-inputs">
              <input class="username" type="text" placeholder="Username" />
              <input class="age" type="number" placeholder="Age" />
              <input class="signupEmail" type="email" placeholder="Email" />
              <input class="signupPassword" type="password"
                placeholder="Password" />
            </div>
            <button class="submitBtn" type="submit">Sign up</button>
            <p>Already have an account? <span class="signupbarlink">Sign in</span></p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="navbar-area">
      <div class="navbar">
        <nav class="navbar-nav">
          <div class="barnav">
            <div class="brandLogo">
              <img src="/assets/taskImg2.jpg" alt="brand logo" />
            </div>
            <div class="bar">
              <span class="barIcon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
              </span>
              <span class="crossBarIcon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i>
              </span>
            </div></div>
          <div class="nav-links">
            <ul>
              <div class="nav-link-div">
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i></span>
                <li class="nav-link">Home</li>
              </div>
              <div class="nav-link-div">
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-address-card"></i></span>
                <li class="nav-link">About Us</li>
              </div>
              <div class="nav-link-div">
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-list-check"></i></span>
                <li class="nav-link">Contact Us</li>
              </div>
              <div class="loginBtn nav-link-div">
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-right-to-bracket"></i></span>
                <li class="nav-link">Sign in</li>
              </div>
              <div class="signupbtn nav-link-div">
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus"></i></span>
                <li class="nav-link">Start For Free</li>
              </div>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="main-area">
      <main>
        <div class="main-div">
          <div class="info-heading">
            <span>Create,</span>
            <span>Focus,</span>
            <span> And Succeed</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-text">
            <p>
              The key is in not spending time, but in investing it wisely and
              orderely
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="joinBtn">
            <span>
              Start For Free
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sec-div">
          <div class="div1-area">
            <div class="div1-img">
              <img src="./assets/task1Img.webp" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="div1-info">
              <h1 >
                <p style="font-size: 30px;">
                Get Your task organized at one place.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 30px;">Start your new journey today with task manager</p>
              </h1>
              <p style="margin-top: 8px;">Your task list is automatically sorted into Today, Upcoming and
                custom Filter views to help you focus on your most important
                things.

              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="div2-area">
            <div class="div2-info">
              <h1 style="font-size: 35px;"><p style="font-size: 40px;">Get your Task Manager.</p>
               <p style="font-size: 35px;">Make your life fast forward with Task Manager App.</p></h1>
              <p style="margin-top: 8px;">
               Get daily update of your tasks, Never miss out any opportunity adn Use your time efficiently.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="div2-img">
              <img src="./assets/task2Img.webp" alt="" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="last-div">
            <div class="lastdiv-img">
              <img src="./assets/lastTaskImg.webp" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="lastdiv-quote">
              <h2 style="font-size: 30px;">
               You get to decide where your time goes. You can either spend it moving forward, or you can spend it putting out fires. You decide. And if you donâ€™t decide, others will decide for you.
              </h2>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </section>
    {{>footer}}
    <script src="/js/index.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>